data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bath bi-level with 2 car attached garage in Washington Local School District. This traditional-style gem has been thoughtfully updated with granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, and remodeled bathrooms. HUGE 4th bedroom on the lower level with large walk in closet. The spacious lower level family room walks right out to the backyard which leads right to luxurious above ground pool with a newer deck, creating an oasis for relaxation and entertainment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this your dream home - schedule your showing today!"
